OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:
OL,6,FSunshine and showers through Monday.
OL,7,FDrier and brighter on Tuesday, ahead
OL,8,Fof rain arriving later in the day.
OL,9,FWetter and windier again on Wednesday.
OL,10,FTemperatures trending up a little.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
